my all-time idol,

06:10.974 --> 06:13.024
the Karate Kid!

06:13.026 --> 06:15.009
NARRATOR: The Karate Kid
<i>was an uplifting '80s classic</i>

06:15.011 --> 06:17.145
<i>about a teen,</i>
<i>played by Ralph Macchio,</i>

06:17.147 --> 06:20.365
<i>who defeats the local jerk,</i>
<i>played by William Zabka.</i>

06:20.367 --> 06:22.734
<i>At least, that's how</i>
<i>most people saw it.</i>

06:22.736 --> 06:24.653
Here he is, just as hot

06:24.655 --> 06:28.123
as when his <i>Tiger Beat</i>
photo spread gave a young girl

06:28.125 --> 06:29.324
the courage to explore

06:29.326 --> 06:31.710
the suddenly unfamiliar
topography

06:31.712 --> 06:34.245
of her changing body...

06:34.247 --> 06:37.666
the Karate Kid!

06:37.668 --> 06:38.967
Hey, Barney. It's Ralph.

06:38.969 --> 06:40.302
Listen,
it's always flattering...

06:40.304 --> 06:41.553
No!

06:42.471 --> 06:43.871
I hate Ralph Macchio!

06:43.873 --> 06:46.174
I hate him, hate him, hate him!

06:46.176 --> 06:48.209
He is not the Karate Kid!

06:48.211 --> 06:50.395
The Karate Kid
was William Zabka,

06:50.397 --> 06:53.064
star pupil
of the Cobra Kai Dojo,

06:53.066 --> 06:54.599
who this monster

06:54.601 --> 06:55.600
defeated
with a cheap,

06:55.602 --> 06:57.885
<i>illegal</i> head-kick

06:57.887 --> 07:03.108
