07:26.133 --> 07:27.749
like my bachelor party--
strippers, booze,

07:27.751 --> 07:29.267
definitely no hand stuff--
wink-wink--

07:29.269 --> 07:33.021
it is gonna be in--
wait for it-- credible.

07:33.023 --> 07:34.055
Incredible!

07:34.057 --> 07:34.973
