even <i>get</i> a stripper?

07:44.317 --> 07:45.483
Bro.
(chuckling)

07:45.485 --> 07:46.735
Bro.

07:46.737 --> 07:48.436
Of course we
got a stripper.

07:48.438 --> 07:50.538
