07:59.282 --> 08:02.283
in the sensibly-priced business
hotel outside Atlantic City.

08:04.119 --> 08:05.620
Who is it?

08:05.622 --> 08:07.789
WOMAN: Police. We got
a noise complaint from...

08:07.791 --> 08:10.842
